Responsive Django Admin
=======================

If you're looking for a version compatible with Django 1.8 just install **0.3.7.1**.

Features
--------

* Responsive
* Sidebar Menu
* Easy install / setup
* Support Django **1.11** and **2.1**
* Bootstrap 3
* Python 3


Screenshots
